desc: Award-winning cookery school in Wilmslow, Cheshire, offering daytime and evening classes and bespoke lessons to all ability levels.

layout.text: Welcome to Wilmslow Kitchen Cookery in the heart of Cheshire. We have courses for beginners, experienced home cooks, professionals and kids. Whether it's your first time learning to cook or you want to take your skills to the next level we have a course for you.
